Class DrinkVariation

java.lang.Object
app.DrinkVariation
public class DrinkVariation extends Object
Represents a specific variation of a drink with customizable attributes. This class encapsulates drink ID, size, sweetness level, ice level, and topping ID to define a unique drink configuration.
